sudo apt install node-js
sudo apt intall code # VisualStudioCode

npm init 			# Create a default package.json

npm install @types/node
npm install typescript		# not globally
tsc --init			# Create a default tsconfig.json


Turn on SSH
Generate a new ssh key
Name the key something beside id_rsa (it will appear in your ~/.ssh folder)
Add the public key to GitHub
On your terminal, add the ssh identity to ssh-agent with:
	ssh-add ~/.ssh/the_other_name 
